  "text": "Agent has two types of behavior: one is the micro action taken at every state, which is similar to muscle activity, called reaction; another is the change of trend in reactions taken over a period of time, which is similar to thought of human, called planning [CITATION_1] . For the agent in maze, reaction can be its every little moving step and planning can be its every determination of the position it should reach next.",
